  "tasbihatZahraOriginLabel": "Chiyambi",
  "tasbihatZahraHadith": "Lady Fatima al-Zahra (sa) anapempha Mtumiki ﷺ wantchito. Iye anati: \"Kodi sindikuwonetsa chinthu chabwino kuposa chimenecho? Werengani Subḥānallāh ka 33, Alḥamdulillāh ka 33, ndi Allāhu Akbar ka 34 pambuyo pa pemphero lililonse. Zimenezo ndi zabwino kuposa wantchito.\"",
