  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiNote": "Aliyense amene awerenga Āyat al-Kursī pambuyo pa pemphero lililonse lovomerezeka, palibe chomulekanitsa ndi Paradiso kupatula imfa. Imam al-Bāqir (a) anati ndi imodzi mwa ayah zazikulu kwambiri mu Qur'an.",
