  "tasbihatDuaSalawatSource": "Imam al-Ṣādiq (a) — Al-Kāfī",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatNote": "Kutumiza madalitso kwa Mneneri ﷺ ndi banja lake loyera (Āl Muḥammad) kumalimbikitsidwa kuti kumalize dua iliyonse. Imam al-Ṣādiq (a) anati: \"Dua iliyonse imayembekezera mpaka mutatumiza ṣalawāt kwa Muḥammad ndi banja lake.\"",
